name: Mia the Necklace
description:
Mia is a hand-embroidered necklace that features cross-stitch technique. The back of the textile pendant is from shiny white lamé with tiny gold dots. It is reinforced so it does not creases during wear.

name: Noe the Headdress
description:
Noe is a versatile, hand-emboridered accessory using cross-stitch technique. Thanks to shiny satin ribbons that  are 50 cm/ 19.7 inches long on each side, it can be used as a headdres, a necklace or a belt embellishing a simple blouse or dress. 

The ribbon can be easily swapped for a different color to fit your hair, outfit and mood. 

The size of the headdress itself is approximately 12.5 x 3 cm (4.9" x 1.2") The back side of the headdres features shiny white lamé fabric with tiny golden dots.

For more details and pictures, please visit: kahlel.tumblr.com
